org.kquiet.browser

Interface AddableActionSequence

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ActionComposer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractActionComposer, BasicActionComposer, IfThenElse

    public interface AddableActionSequence
    An AddableActionSequence is a sequence of actions which supports add operations.
    Author:
    Kimberly
